SUMMARY:Quantum Gong Bath Meditation with Alicia M__ Ri Atu M__: Whippersnappers Space at Brockwell Lido
LOCATION:Brockwell Lido, Dulwich Road, SE24 0PA
DESCRIPTION:We hope you can join us for what promises to be an amazing, first-ever Festival soundbath. It might even change your life!

With powerful quantum gong baths, mystical guided meditation, light language and more, Alicia Ma Ri Atu Ma's HUSH HOUR is all about making time for YOU. A musician, sonic artist, nature lover and creative all-rounder, Alicia___s live Festival session will be as much an intimate performance as a transformative, immersive soundscape with healing instruments, quantum technology, percussion, and voice.

Just a few HUSH HOUR testimonials:

&quot;The gongs are strong Alicia and what you do has a depth to it that becomes inexplicable!&quot;

&quot;You have an amazing voice, both spoken and singing&quot;

&quot;I've been to MANY gong baths. This was the best l've ever experienced&quot;

&quot;The combination of relaxation with meditation and being taken on a healing journey (of the imagination) is very powerful, and I felt safe and nurtured.&quot;

&quot;:) ___Thank you so much! That felt really SACRED___.&quot;

___The first time I came, I was high for 2 days!___
